ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectNisga'a Final Agreement, British Columbia
PrecisOrder amending the NISGA'A FINAL AGREEMENT in order to make changes to the boundary of the Nisga'a Memorial Lava Bed Park (British Columbia) by carving out a corridor across the Park through which BC Hydro will construct the Northwest Transmission Line.
